r image.", "part2": "She is seated on a white wicker chair in a sunlit garden, wearing a Zimmermann white floral-print cotton midi dress with puff sleeves, hands folded demurely in her lap. Her expression is a practiced mask of sweet vulnerability — wide doe eyes glistening as if on the verge of grateful tears, a gentle closed-lip smile, head tilted slightly. But her pupils carry an almost imperceptible reptilian coldness if one looks closely. Soft white flowers frame her. The background is a bright, airy garden terrace bathed in golden-hour light, softly blurred.", "part4": "Shot on 35mm film, visible grain, Arri Alexa 65 aesthetic, warm diffused golden-hour key light with subtle overexposure on highlights, cinematic shallow depth of field, character design sheet feel --ar 2:3 --v 7.0 --style raw"}, "negative_prompt": null}, {"prompt": "A raw, hyper-realistic cinematic three-quarter portrait shot of Adrian Winter, a 26-year-old man with refined, clean-cut good looks. He has fair pale skin, intelligent but emotionally hollow light brown eyes behind elegant thin gold-rimmed round spectacles, neatly styled sandy-brown hair parted to the side, a slender elegant build, and classically handsome features — the archetypal trustworthy gentleman whose signature warm smile never quite reaches his eyes.\n\n风格：He is standing in a warmly lit study, wearing a perfectly pressed light-gray Ermenegildo Zegna bespoke suit over a pale blue oxford shirt with no tie, top button undone. One hand holds a leather-bound book casually. His expression is his trademark gentle, approachable smile — lips curved softly upward, brows relaxed — yet his light brown eyes remain flat, calculating, and utterly devoid of warmth, creating an uncanny valley of trustworthiness. The background is a richly appointed library with mahogany shelves and soft lamp light, heavily blurred.\n\n参考风格：\nShot on 35mm film, visible grain, Arri Alexa 65 aesthetic, warm tungsten key light with soft shadows, cinematic shall