ge, clear light blue, set in slightly sunken sockets, filled with a melancholy and timid ''grown-up'' wisdom.", "part2": "She is sitting, her tiny frail frame completely swallowed by multiple layers of thick, heavy, pilled wool blankets with visible stains. Underneath, an oversized, coarse, faded old sweater is visible, with sleeves so long they cover her hands. One small hand is instinctively clutching a silver cross necklace as if holding onto a lifeline. Her mouth is slightly open, gasping for breath with visible effort in her chest. Her brow is slightly furrowed in an anxious, ''sorry to be a burden'' expression.", "part4": "The background is a cold, dim, decaying bedroom with peeling paint, heavily blurred and out of focus. Shot on 35mm film, visible grain, Arri Alexa 65 aesthetic, melancholic dim lighting. --ar 2:3 --v 7.0 --style raw"}, "negative_prompt": null}, {"prompt": "A raw, hyper-realistic cinematic three-quarter portrait shot of Elena Voss, a 26-year-old Caucasian mixed-race woman with warm olive-toned skin and mesmerizing frosty grey cat-shaped eyes. She has thick, voluminous jet-black curly hair cascading past her shoulders, full sensuous M-shaped lips painted in deep crimson, high cheekbones, and a sculpted hourglass figure that exudes both elegance and lethal allure.\n\n风格：She stands with poised, predatory confidence, wearing a Valentino scarlet-red haute couture backless gown that drapes over her curves like liquid fire. Her gaze is cold, calculating, and dangerously seductive — the look of a Bengal leopard cat about to strike. One hand rests lightly at her side, fingers adorned with a single statement ring. Her expression carries a subtle duality: outward breathtaking beauty masking inner ruthlessness, the transformation from a frightened Ragdoll cat into an elegant huntress now complete.\n\n参考风格：\nThe background is a dimly lit opulent ballroom with golden chandeliers and marble columns, heavily blurred and out of focus. Shot on 35mm film, visib