en highlights sculpting her olive skin. --ar 2:3 --v 7.0 --style raw", "line_no": 2, "ext_params": {"count": 1}, "source_mode": "template", "prompt_blocks": {"part1": "A raw, hyper-realistic cinematic three-quarter portrait shot", "part2": "Elena Voss, a 26-year-old Caucasian mixed-heritage woman with warm olive-toned skin and piercing frost-grey cat-shaped eyes that gleam with cold, predatory calculation. She has voluminous, dense black curly hair cascading past her shoulders, full sculptural M-shaped lips painted in deep crimson, and a striking hourglass silhouette. She wears a Valentino crimson haute couture backless gown that drapes over her figure like liquid fire. Her posture is poised and lethal, chin slightly raised, one hand resting elegantly at her collarbone. Her expression is a dangerously serene half-smile — the look of a woman who has transformed from a frightened prey into an apex predator. Her eyes hold razor-sharp intelligence masked behind sensual allure, a beast-tamer studying her quarry.", "part4": "The background is a dimly lit opulent ballroom with warm amber candlelight reflections and dark mahogany paneling, heavily blurred and out of focus. Shot on 35mm film, visible grain, Arri Alexa 65 aesthetic, dramatic chiaroscuro lighting with warm golden highlights sculpting her olive skin. --ar 2:3 --v 7.0 --style raw"}, "negative_prompt": null}, {"prompt": "A raw, hyper-realistic cinematic three-quarter portrait shot\n\n风格：Caius King, a 30-year-old man with an intensely striking mixed-heritage appearance, deep olive-toned skin, and chilling ice-blue eyes that burn with possessive, barely-restrained menace. He has short-cropped jet-black hair, a sharp chiseled jawline with faint stubble, and a powerful inverted-triangle physique standing over 190cm tall, radiating raw masculine dominance. He wears an impeccably tailored charcoal Brunello Cucinelli three-piece suit with a subtle sheen, the top button of his shirt undone, a Patek Philippe watch glintin