 blue-black heavy wool with faded silver runic embroidery along the hem and cuffs, over a dark grey inner tunic belted with a worn leather belt bearing a tarnished silver wolf-head buckle. Heavy dark leather boots, worn and aged. Around his neck a chain of old silver medallions with clan symbols. Gnarled hands with prominent veins, holding a carved wooden staff with a silver wolf-head finial. Overall aesthetic is ancient druidic elder meets gothic patriarch, wise and foreboding. European-American dark fantasy cinematic realism, muted dark color palette with midnight blues, aged silvers, and weathered earth tones.\n\n人设：老祭司艾尔德里奇（Eldritch）\n\n参考风格：\n欧美暗黑奇幻风格。布莱克伍德家族的长老祭司，知晓族群所有秘密。引导伊芙琳觉醒银血之力，教导她控制狼人意志的方法（共鸣而非统治）。揭示银血家族历史、古老契约真相，提供母亲项链、塞琳娜之血、自身眼泪三样觉醒要素。在关键时刻识破达米安召唤远古血魔的禁忌之术。", "line_no": 5, "ext_params": {"count": 1}, "source_mode": "template", "prompt_blocks": {"part1": "请生成一张高完成度角色定妆照资产图，角色居中正面站立或微侧身展示，完整清晰呈现人物外形设定与服装造型，强调\"角色资产展示\"用途而非剧情场景。画面重点突出人物本体，五官精致稳定，脸型清晰，发型完整，发丝细腻，妆容准确，表情自然克制，眼神有神但不过度夸张。服装结构完整可辨，层次清楚，材质真实，纹样与配饰位置准确，鞋履、腰饰、头饰、手部细节齐全，整体设计统一且便于后续持续复用。光影干净通透，色彩统一高级，边缘清晰，无过强动态，无大幅透视变形。背景使用纯色、浅灰或干净渐变背景，可带极弱环境光，不添加复杂场景，确保人物轮廓完整突出。构图为标准角色定妆照/角色设定图形式，适合角色库归档与后续批量镜头统一。", "part2": "Elder Priest Eldritch, elderly male approximately 70-80 years old, ancient elder and keeper of secrets of the Blackwood werewolf clan. Tall but slightly stooped with age, gaunt and weathered frame suggesting great age and endurance. Long narrow face deeply lined with wrinkles, sunken cheeks, prominent brow, a long aquiline nose. Pale grey-blue eyes that are sharp, knowing, and carry centuries of hidden wisdom, slightly clouded at the edges. Long silver-white hair flowing past his shoulders, thin and wispy, with a receding hairline. A long silver-white beard, neatly kept, reaching mid-chest. Skin deeply weathered, parchment-like, with age spots on hands and temples. Expression solemn, measured, with quiet authority and a hint of sorrow. Wearing layered dark robes — an outer long hooded cloak i