黑色改良制服，配戴一柄古朴武士刀', NULL, 'midj_default', 'SUCCESS', 1, 3, '2026-04-27 18:36:47.779', NULL, NULL, '{"cfg": 7, "size": "1024x1536", "count": 2, "steps": 30}', NULL, '2026-04-27 18:26:45.943', '2026-04-27 18:37:36.758', NULL, '{"part1": "樱花代表，千岛凛，28岁，女性，精英学者兼武士，来自学阀高层家族，精通历史与战术", "part2": "身高165cm，身形纤细如柳，面容清冷似霜，黑色眼睛锐利如刀，黑色长发束成一丝不苟的高马尾", "part3": null, "part4": "黑色改良制服，配戴一柄古朴武士刀", "source_mode": "template"}', '角色3', NULL, '{"name": "角色3", "gender": "unknown"}', NULL);
INSERT INTO "public"."job_items" VALUES (72, 17, 'IT20260424034022XM6NE', 1, '请生成一张高完成度角色定妆照资产图，角色居中正面站立或微侧身展示，完整清晰呈现人物外形设定与服装造型，强调"角色资产展示"用途而非剧情场景。画面重点突出人物本体，五官精致稳定，脸型清晰，发型完整，发丝细腻，妆容准确，表情自然克制，眼神有神但不过度夸张。服装结构完整可辨，层次清楚，材质真实，纹样与配饰位置准确，鞋履、腰饰、头饰、手部细节齐全，整体设计统一且便于后续持续复用。光影干净通透，色彩统一高级，边缘清晰，无过强动态，无大幅透视变形。背景使用纯色、浅灰或干净渐变背景，可带极弱环境光，不添加复杂场景，确保人物轮廓完整突出。构图为标准角色定妆照/角色设定图形式，适合角色库归档与后续批量镜头统一。

风格：Evelyn Carter, 26-year-old female, New York investigative journalist. Caucasian, sharp and determined facial features, high cheekbones, defined jawline, intelligent piercing eyes with a faint silver glint in the pupils hinting at latent supernatural heritage. Medium-length dark brown hair with subtle silver-tipped ends, slightly tousled and natural, parted to one side. Light natural makeup, minimal eyeshadow, nude lips, a few small scratches or healing marks on her temple suggesting recent ordeal. Expression resolute, composed, with underlying emotional intensity. Wearing a fitted dark olive green field jacket over a black crew-neck top, slim dark jeans, brown leather ankle boots with low heels. Around her neck a delicate antique silver pendant necklace (her mother''s heirloom) with faint engraved rune-like patterns. A leather crossbody messenger bag slung at her hip. Hands with short practical nails, one wrist bearing a simple watch. Overall style is modern urban practical with a touch of gothic undertone, grounded and realistic. European-American dark fantasy aesthetic, cinematic realism, muted cool color palette with desaturated greens and blacks.

人设：伊芙琳·卡特（Evelyn Carter）

参考风格：
欧美暗黑奇幻风格，参考《暮光之城》《吸血鬼日记》氛围。26岁纽约女记者，理性倔强，因调查姐姐塞琳娜失踪来到银溪镇。银血家族最后的继承人，拥有支配狼人意志的觉醒之力。从受害者妹妹成长为觉醒女王，最终以自身之血封印恶魔。瞳孔带淡淡银光，母亲遗留的古银项链是关键道具。', NULL, 'midj_default', 'FAILED', 3, 3, NULL, 'E_PROVIDER_TIMEOUT', 'Model request timeout.', '{"cfg": 7, "size": "1024x1536", "count": 1, "steps": 30}', NULL, '2026-04-24 03:42:39.97', '2026-04-24 16:26:29.234', NULL, '{"part1": "请生成一张高完成度角色定妆照资产图，角色居中正面站立或微侧身展示，完整清晰呈现人物外形设定与服装造型，强调\"角色资产展示\"用途而非剧情场景。画面重点突出人物本体，五官精致稳定，脸型清晰，发型完整，发丝细腻，妆容准确，表情自然克制，眼神有神但不过度夸张。服装结构完整可辨，层次清楚，材质真实，纹样与配饰位置准确，鞋履、腰饰、头饰、手部细节齐全，整体设计统一且便于后续持续复用。光影干净通透，色彩统一高级，边缘清晰，无过强动态，无大幅透视变形。背景使用纯色、浅灰或干净渐变背景，可带极弱环境光，不添加复杂场景，确保人物轮廓完整突出。构图为标准角色定妆照/角色设定图形式，适合角色库归档与后续批量镜头统一。", "part2": "Evelyn Carter, 26-year-old female, New York investigative journalist. Caucasian, sharp and determined facial features, high cheekbones, defined jawline, intelligent piercing eyes with a faint silver glint in the pupils hinting at latent supernatural heritage. Medium-length dark brown hair with subtle silver-tipped ends, slightly tousled and natural, parted to one side. Light natural makeup, minimal eyeshadow, nude lips, a few small scratches or healing marks on her temple suggesting recent ordeal. Expression resolute, composed, with underlying emotional intensity. Wearing a fitted dark olive green field jacket over a black crew-neck top, slim dark jeans, brown leather ankle boots with low heels. Around her neck a delicate antique silver pendant necklace (her mother''s heirloom) with faint engraved rune-like patterns. A leather crossbody messenger bag slung at her hip. Hands with short practical nails, one wrist bearing a simple watch. Overall style is modern urban practical with a touch of gothic undertone, grounded and realistic. European-American dark fantasy aesthetic, cinematic realism, muted cool color palette with desaturated greens and blacks.", "part3": "伊芙琳·卡特（Evelyn Carter）", "part4": "欧美暗黑奇幻风格，参考《暮光之城》《吸血鬼日记》氛围。26岁纽约女记者，理性倔强，因调查姐姐塞琳娜失踪来到银溪镇。银血家族最后的继承人，拥有支配狼人意志的觉醒之力。从受害者妹妹成长为觉醒女王，最终以自身之血封印恶魔。瞳孔带淡淡银光，母亲遗留的古银项链是关键道具。", "source_mode": "template"}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO "public"."job_items" VALUES (185, 49, 'IT20260427182148MQXTV', 1, 'Lu Guan, 31-year-old male geography student and protagonist, determined and resolute demeanor

风格：178cm tall, slender build, handsome and refined face, black eyes, black short hair streaked with a few silver-white strands

参考风格：
wearing a slightly worn but clean dark gray mandarin-collar jacket, minimalist and practical style', NULL, 'midj_default', 'SUCCESS', 0, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"cfg": 7, "size": "1024x1536", "count": 1, "steps": 30}', NULL, '2026-04-27 18:24:00.106', '2026-04-27 18:26:43.104', NULL, '{"part1": "Lu Guan, 31-year-old male geography student and protagonist, determined and resolute demeanor", "part2": "178cm tall, slender build, handsome and refined face, black eyes, black short hair streaked with a few silver-white strands", "part3": null, "part4": "wearing a slightly worn but clean dark gray mandarin-collar jacket, minimalist and practical style", "source_mode": "template"}', '角色1', NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO "public"."job_items" VALUES (74, 17, 'IT20260424034022XMXIZ', 3, '请生成一张高完成度角色定妆照资产图，角色居中正面站立或微侧身展示，完整清晰呈现人物外形设定与服装造型，强调"角色资产展示"用途而非剧情场景。画面重点突出人物本体，五官精致稳定，脸型清晰，发型完整，发丝细腻，妆容准确，表情自然克制，眼神有神但不过度夸张。服装结构完整可辨，层次清楚，材质真实，纹样与配饰位置准确，鞋履、腰饰、头饰、手部细节齐全，整体设计统一且便于后续持续复用。光影干净通透，色彩统一高级，边缘清晰，无过强动态，无大幅透视变形。背景使用纯色、浅灰或干净渐变背景，可带极弱环境光，不添加复杂场景，确保人物轮廓完整突出。构图为标准角色定妆照/角色设定图形式，适合角色库归档与后续批量镜头统一。

风格：Damien Grey, 28-year-old male, half-brother of Lucas Blackwood, werewolf pack traitor and ambitious schemer. Tall and lean, slightly less bulky than Lucas but equally striking. Devilishly handsome with a charismatic, seductive quality. Refined angular features, high cheekbones, narrow predatory eyes with amber-gold irises that suggest cunning and danger. A charming yet unsettling smile, perfectly symmetrical face. Dark auburn-brown hair, medium length, slicked back with a polished sophisticated style. Clean-shaven, immaculate grooming. Skin slightly warmer-toned than Lucas, with a subtle golden undertone. Expression composed with a knowing smirk, radiating controlled menace beneath surface charm. Wearing an impeccably tailored dark burgundy three-piece suit with black satin lapels, crisp white dress shirt, thin black silk tie, polished black Oxford shoes. A dark leather glove on one hand, the other hand bare revealing sharp manicured nails. A small silver bullet pendant hanging from his vest pocket chain as a provocative accessory. Overall aesthetic is refined dark elegance, the charismatic villain archetype, blending aristocratic sophistication with predatory edge. European-American dark fantasy cinematic realism, warm-dark color palette with deep burgundies, blacks, and golds.

人设：达米安·格雷（Damien Grey）

参考风格：
欧美暗黑奇幻风格，参考《吸血鬼日记》反派氛围。28岁，卢卡斯同父异母兄长，野心勃勃的魅力反派。狼群中的叛徒，杀害塞琳娜以夺取狼群领导权，勾结圣银骑士团猎人组织。最终召唤远古血魔禁忌之术，化为双翼恶魔形态。表面迷人优雅，内心冷酷算计，给伊芙琳银色子弹实为布局。', NULL, 'midj_default', 'SUCCESS', 0, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"cfg": 7, "size": "1024x1536", "count": 1, "steps": 30}', NULL, '2026-04-24 03:42:39.97', '2026-04-24 03:43:45.327', NULL, '{"part1": "请生成一张高完成度角色定妆照资产图，角色居中正面站立或微侧身展示，完整清晰呈现人物外形设定与服装造型，强调\"角色资产展示\"用途而非剧情场景。画面重点突出人物本体，五官精致稳定，脸型清晰，发型完整，发丝细腻，妆容准确，表情自然克制，眼神有神但不过度夸张。服装结构完整可辨，层次清楚，材质真实，纹样与配饰位置准确，鞋履、腰饰、头饰、手部细节齐全，整体设计统一且便于后续持续复用。光影干净通透，色彩统一高级，边缘清晰，无过强动态，无大幅透视变形。背景使用纯色、浅灰或干净渐变背景，可带极弱环境光，不添加复杂场景，确保人物轮廓完整突出。构图为标准角色定妆照/角色设定图形式，适合角色库归档与后续批量镜头统一。", "part2": "Damien Grey, 28-year-old male, half-brother of Lucas Blackwood, werewolf pack traitor and ambitious schemer. Tall and lean, slightly less bulky than Lucas but equally striking. Devilishly handsome with a charismatic, seductive quality. Refined angular features, high cheekbones, narrow predatory eyes with amber-gold irises that suggest cunning and danger. A charming yet unsettling smile, perfectly symmetrical face. Dark auburn-brown hair, medium length, slicked back with a polished sophisticated style. Clean-shaven, immaculate grooming. Skin slightly warmer-toned than Lucas, with a subtle golden undertone. Expression composed with a knowing smirk, radiating controlled menace beneath surface charm. Wearing an impeccably tailored dark burgundy three-piece suit with black satin lapels, crisp white dress shirt, thin black silk tie, polished black Oxford shoes. A dark leather glove on one hand, the other hand bare revealing sharp manicured nails. A small silver bullet pendant hanging from his vest pocket chain as a provocative accessory. Overall aesthetic is refined dark elegance, the charismatic villain archetype, blending aristocratic sophistication with predatory edge. European-American dark fantasy cinematic realism, warm-dark color palette with deep burgundies, blacks, and golds.", "part3": "达米安·格雷（Damien Grey）", "part4": "欧美暗黑奇幻风格，参考《吸血鬼